import React, { Component } from 'react';
import { ImageBackground, StyleSheet,Image, Text, TouchableOpacity, View } from 'react-native';
import { LinearGradient } from 'expo-linear-gradient';
import { TextInput } from 'react-native-gesture-handler';
import Checkbox from 'expo-checkbox';





export default class Login extends Component{


    constructor(props){
        super(props)
        this.state={
            email:'',
            password:''

        }
    }


    render(){
        return(
           <View style={{
            flexDirection:'column',
            height:"86%"
           }}>
            <View style={{height:"5%",width:"100%",backgroundColor:"#880606"}}></View>
            <View style={{
                height:'20%',
                width:'100%',
                flexDirection:'row',
                backgroundColor:'#ffffff'
            }}>
                
                <View>
                    <ImageBackground source={require('./images/WhatsApp_Image_2023-02-28_at_5.37.06_PM-removebg-preview.png')}
                    style={{height:'90%',
                    width:190,
                    marginTop:15
                    }}
                    
                    ></ImageBackground>
                    
                </View>
                <View style={{justifyContent:"center"}}>
                <Text style={{fontFamily:'YanoneKaffeesatz',fontSize:75,color:'#880606',paddingTop:10,fontWeight:"bold"}}>EMAAN INSTITUTE</Text>
                <Text style={{fontFamily:'YanoneKaffeesatz',fontSize:48,color:'#880606',paddingTop:1,fontWeight:"bold"}}>OF MANAGEMENT & SCIENCE</Text>

                </View>
                <View style={{alignItems:'center',justifyContent:'center', backgroundColor:'transparent',height:40, width:'12%',alignSelf:'center',marginRight:10,marginLeft:3}}>
                        <TouchableOpacity style={{width:"100%",height:"100%",justifyContent:"center",alignItems:"center"}}>
                        <Text style={{fontFamily:"YanoneKaffeesatz",fontWeight:"600",alignSelf:"center",color:"#880606",fontSize:22}}>About</Text>

                        </TouchableOpacity>

                    
                    
                </View>

                <View style={{alignItems:'center',justifyContent:'center', backgroundColor:'transparent',height:40, width:'12%',alignSelf:'center',marginRight:10}}>
                        <TouchableOpacity style={{width:"100%",height:"100%",justifyContent:"center",alignItems:"center"}}>
                        <Text style={{fontFamily:"YanoneKaffeesatz",fontWeight:"600",alignSelf:"center",color:"#880606",fontSize:22}}>Contact</Text>

                        </TouchableOpacity>

                    
                    
                </View>

                <View style={{alignItems:'center',justifyContent:'center', backgroundColor:'transparent',height:40, width:'12%',alignSelf:'center',marginRight:20}}>
                        <TouchableOpacity style={{width:"100%",height:"100%",justifyContent:"center",alignItems:"center"}}>
                        <Text style={{fontFamily:"YanoneKaffeesatz",fontWeight:"600",alignSelf:"center",color:"#880606",fontSize:22}}>Admissions</Text>

                        </TouchableOpacity>

                    
                    
                </View>



                
                


                
                
                
                </View>
                <View style={{height:"5%",width:"100%",backgroundColor:"#880606"}}></View>
                <View style={{height:"100%",width:"100%"}}>
                    <Image source={require('./images/311381381_982955666431550_812384766897590576_n.jpg')}
                    style={{
                        width: '100%',
                        height: undefined,
                        aspectRatio: 1,
                        resizeMode:"contain"
                    }}
                    >
                        
                        
                        
                        
                         </Image>
                </View>


           </View>
        );

    }
}

    box: {
        width: '100%',

        borderRadius:4

        flexDirection:'row',

        shadowOpacity: 0.28,

        borderRightColor:'#103a5e',
        justifyContent:'flex-end',

      imageview:{

      inputViewA:{

        justifyContent:"space-evenly",
        backgroundColor: "#ffffff",
        borderRadius: 28,
        width: "15%",
        height: 55,
      },
      inputViewB:{

        backgroundColor: "#ffffff",

        height: 55,
      },
      TextInput:{
        alignContent:"center",

        alignItems:"center",
        fontFamily:"monospace",
        width:"100%",
        paddingLeft:8,
        height:55
        
        
  
      },
      imageviewbackground:{
        height:1000,

})
